OL,5, Limits have been placed on the amount  
OL,6, of books convicted terrorists in       
OL,7, England and Wales can keep in their    
OL,8, prison cells.                          
OL,10,FExtremists will also now be banned from
OL,11,Ftaking a "leading role" in religious   
OL,12,Fservices under the new measures.       
OL,14,FIt follows a 2022 report which raised  
OL,15,Fconcerns about radicalisation and      
OL,16,FIslamist gangs in prisons.             
OL,18,FNew Justice Secretary Alex Chalk said  
OL,19,Fthe changes would stop terrorists      
OL,20,Fadvancing "their own sinister agenda". 
